'''氧化钡'''（[[化学式|化学式]]：[[钡|Ba]][[氧|O]]）是[[钡|钡]]的正常[[氧化物|氧化物]]，为白色固体。它可由钡在[[氧气|氧气]]中燃烧，或[[:Category:钡化合物|钡盐]]热分解制得：<ref>{{cite web  | title = Compounds of barium: barium (II) oxide  | work = Web Elements  | publisher = The University of Sheffield  | date = 2007-01-26  | url = http://www.webelements.com/webelements/compounds/text/Ba/Ba1O1-1304285.html  | accessdate = 2007-02-22  | archive-date = 2006-11-10  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061110011621/http://www.webelements.com/webelements/compounds/text/Ba/Ba1O1-1304285.html  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

: 2Ba + O<sub>2</sub> → 2BaO
: BaCO<sub>3</sub> → BaO + CO<sub>2</sub>

与水反应生成[[氢氧化钡|氢氧化钡]]：
: BaO + H<sub>2</sub>O → Ba(OH)<sub>2</sub>

==用途==
氧化钡可用作[[热阴极|热阴极]]及[[阴极射线管|阴极射线管]]中的涂层以及生产特定种类的玻璃，如光学[[冕牌玻璃|冕牌玻璃]]。以前曾用[[氧化铅|氧化铅]]于此用途，但由于氧化铅不仅提高了[[折射率|折射率]]，还提高了[[色散率|色散率]]，因此现已被只提高折射率的氧化钡取代。<ref>{{cite web  | title = Barium Oxide (chemical compound)  | work = Encyclopædia Britanica  | publisher = Encyclopædia Britanica  | date = 2007  | url = http://www.britannica.com/eb/topic-53368/barium-oxide  | accessdate = 2007-02-19  | archive-date = 2007-07-15  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070715151103/http://www.britannica.com/eb/topic-53368/barium-oxide  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>此外，氧化钡还可用作[[乙氧基化|乙氧基化]]反应的催化剂，催化[[环氧乙烷|环氧乙烷]]与[[醇|醇]]在150-200°C反应。<ref>{{Citation  | last = Nield  | first = Gerald  | last2 = Washecheck  | first2 = Paul  | last3 = Yang  | first3 = Kang  | title = United States Patent 4210764  | date = 05-04  | year = 1979  | url = http://www.freepatentsonline.com/4210764.html  | accessdate = 2007-02-20  | archive-date = 2007-05-06  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070506121041/http://www.freepatentsonline.com/4210764.html  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

==安全==
氧化钡具刺激性，与皮肤、眼部接触或吸入会造成疼痛和红肿。吞食危险更大，会导致[[恶心|恶心]]、[[腹泻|腹泻]]、肌肉[[麻痹|麻痹]]和心律失常，严重时可能致死。

氧化钡同样对[[水生生物|水生生物]]有害。<ref>{{cite web  | title = Barium Oxide (ICSC)  | publisher = IPCS  | date = October 1999  | url = http://www.inchem.org/documents/icsc/icsc/eics0778.htm  | accessdate = 2007-02-19  | archive-date = 2007-02-26  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070226194744/http://www.inchem.org/documents/icsc/icsc/eics0778.htm  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>

